OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1778868675
OL,3,CPrivate ambulance service at risk of
OL,4,Ccollapse over alleged #1m tax bill
OL,6,FA private ambulance company that
OL,7,Fdrives patients across Bristol, North
OL,8,FSomerset and South Gloucestershire is
OL,9,Fat risk of collapse, over an alleged
OL,10,F#1million tax bill.
OL,12,FPeople who rely on Bristol Ambulance
OL,13,Fhave been advised to find other ways
OL,14,Fto travel.
OL,16,FHis Majesty's Revenue and Customs
OL,17,F(HMRC) has served the company with a
OL,18,Fwinding-up petition. This is an
OL,19,Fapplication brought to the High Court
OL,20,Fto close down a company.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
