FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1778868675
OL,3,CPrivate ambulance service at risk of
OL,4,Ccollapse over alleged #1m tax bill
OL,6,FDirector of Bristol Ambulance Shaun
OL,7,FPillinger told staff in a company
OL,8,Fnotice that their "wages... through
OL,9,Fthe end of May, (would be) fully
OL,10,Fsupported".
OL,12,FHe said there were "no planned changes
OL,13,Fto current roles or responsibilities
OL,14,Fat this stage" and any future changes
OL,15,Fwould be made with "minimal
OL,16,Fdisruption" to staff and patients.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1778868675
OL,3,CPrivate ambulance service at risk of
OL,4,Ccollapse over alleged #1m tax bill
OL,6,FMr Pillinger added that there had been
OL,7,F"strong interest" from other
OL,8,Forganisations in the sector about
OL,9,Fpotentially investing in the company
OL,10,For acquiring it.
OL,12,FHe said an external team were working
OL,13,Fon getting the court proceedings
OL,14,Fadjourned while talks with potential
OL,15,Finvestors continue.
OL,17,FA spokesperson for the NHS Bristol,
OL,18,FNorth Somerset and South
OL,19,FGloucestershire integrated care board
OL,20,Fsaid they were aware of the winding-up
OL,21,Fpetition.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
