OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1778868675
OL,3,CPrivate ambulance service at risk of
OL,4,Ccollapse over alleged #1m tax bill
OL,6,FThey said: "Local patient transport
OL,7,Fservices continue to be provided on a
OL,8,Fbusiness-as-usual basis, and eligible
OL,9,Fpatients should continue to use the
OL,10,FPatient Transport Hub phone number and
OL,11,Fwebsite as normal to book transport.
OL,13,F"It is possible that delays may be
OL,14,Fexperienced following this
OL,15,Fannouncement and we ask patients to
OL,16,Fconsider using family or alternative
OL,17,Ftransport arrangements where possible.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
